title: Blackjack Card Counting GUI Simulator
description: A GUI simulator that both visualizes and simulates a round of blackjack while also counting cards and uses Monte Carlo to assess the best card counting strategy for blackjack.

title: SDCTA Homelessness Dataset
description: Working as a data science intern at San Diego County Taxpayers' Association, I spearheaded a the homelessness dataset project where we we finetuned a token reader to read documents for philanthropies that taxpayers' dollars go to. Also co-created an XML parser.

title: Power Outage Analysis
description: An analysis using power outage data to assess different potential causes and trends in power outage data.
